cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

This paper deals with sentiment analysis and natural language processing, which are both subfields of computer science. The use of reinforcement learning and neural networks also suggests that this paper could fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), or neural networks (cs.NE). However, since the focus is on language processing, the most likely category is computational linguistics (cs.CL).
